<item>
            <title>[LU-1971] lustre-initialization-1: mkfs.lustre FATAL: Loop device setup for /dev/lvm-MDS/P1 failed: Invalid argument</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1971</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for bobijam &amp;lt;bobijam@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/ffaf3af4-0128-11e2-860a-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/ffaf3af4-0128-11e2-860a-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;16:33:32:Formatting mgs, mds, osts&lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:Format mds1: /dev/lvm-MDS/P1&lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:CMD: client-24vm3 grep -c /mnt/mds1&apos; &apos; /proc/mounts&lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:CMD: client-24vm3 lsmod | grep lnet &amp;gt; /dev/null &amp;amp;&amp;amp; lctl dl | grep &apos; ST &apos;&lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:CMD: client-24vm3 /usr/sbin/mkfs.lustre --mgs --mdt --fsname=lustre --mountfsoptions=errors=remount-ro,iopen_nopriv,user_xattr,acl --param sys.timeout=20 --device-size=-104857 --backfstype ldiskfs --reformat /dev/lvm-MDS/P1&lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:client-24vm3: mkfs.lustre: Unable to create backing store: 2&lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:client-24vm3: mkfs.lustre: Unable to truncate backing store: 22&lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:client-24vm3: &lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:client-24vm3: mkfs.lustre FATAL: Loop device setup for /dev/lvm-MDS/P1 failed: Invalid argument&lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:&lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:   Permanent disk data:&lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:Target:     lustre-MDTffff&lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:Index:      unassigned&lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:Lustre FS:  lustre&lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:Mount type: ldiskfs&lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:Flags:      0x75&lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:              (MDT MGS needs_index first_time update )&lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:Persistent mount opts: errors=remount-ro,iopen_nopriv,user_xattr,acl&lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:Parameters: sys.timeout=20&lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:&lt;br/&gt;
16:33:32:mkfs.lustre: exiting with 22 (Invalid argument)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
